<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI digest — {{ date_cz }}</title>
  <!--[if mso]><noscript><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch></o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml></noscript><![endif]-->
  <style>
    body, table, td, p, a, li { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
    img { border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }

    body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      background-color: #f0eef8;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
                   "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #1a1d23;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f0eef8;
      padding: 24px 12px;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #dddaea;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #7c3aed;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .email-header h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .email-header .subtitle {
      font-size: 13px;
      opacity: .85;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 28px 32px;
    }

    .digest-content h2.digest-h2 {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #5b21b6;
      background-color: #f5f3ff;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
      margin: 20px 0 10px;
    }
    .digest-content h3.digest-h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin: 12px 0 6px;
    }
    .digest-content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .digest-content ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .digest-content ul li {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: #374151;
      padding: 8px 10px 8px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      border-left: 3px solid #ddd8ea;
      background-color: #faf9fc;
      border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .digest-content a {
      color: #7c3aed;
      text-decoration: none;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .digest-content em { color: #6b7280; font-style: italic; }
    .digest-content strong { font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #faf9fc;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e0f0;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #7c3aed;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .email-header, .email-body, .email-footer {
        padding-left: 16px !important;
        padding-right: 16px !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-container">

      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>🤖 AI digest</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">{{ date_cz }}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="digest-content">
          {{ summary | safe }}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="email-footer">
        Automaticky generováno pomocí Gemini AI ze zdrojů OpenAI Blog, Google DeepMind, Hugging Face,
        MIT Technology Review, VentureBeat AI, TechCrunch AI, Ars Technica AI, The Verge AI a Wired AI.<br>
        Pokud nechcete dostávat tento email, odhlaste se u administrátora.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
